  "Message": "feat(cms): auth gate, billing integration, and admin bootstrap\n\n- Add middleware auth gate protecting /admin routes (redirects to /login)\n- Check both revealui-session and revealui-token cookies for auth\n- Remove public / -\u003e /admin redirect (admin no longer default page)\n- Add login, signup, reset-password, and account pages\n- Add Stripe billing routes (checkout, portal, subscription) in CMS and API\n- Add webhook handler for Stripe events\n- Add LicenseProvider and UpgradePrompt components\n- Add license status enforcement middleware in API\n- Add stripe_customer_id column to users schema with migration\n- Add seed-admin.mjs script for bootstrapping production admin user\n- Fix landing pricing CTAs to link to CMS signup\n- Defer ElectricSQL integration to Phase 2 in master plan\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e",
